oji\" /> <br />\n愛若難以放進手裡　何不將這雙手放進心裡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd75574fc392f7b805fa40080612b6191ed94e84","tid":322733,"uid":127216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T06:00:06.000Z","msg":"建議巴打等多兩三日<br />\n如果仲唔覆就開新話題<br />\n但如果佢再hea你 or 已讀不回<br />\n就好放手啦<br />\n下個更可愛呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fccdc23e64de3c19d24e7e6871ab8706f32281ee","tid":322733,"uid":101103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T06:06:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>建議巴打等多兩三日<br />\n如果仲唔覆就開新話題<br />\n但如果佢再hea你 or 已讀不回<br />\n就好放手啦<br />\n下個更可愛呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n之前大家幾岩傾都係假象，<br />\nmaybe都只係我一廂情願，<br />\n我唔想做個chur人既毒撚，<br />\n<br />\n多謝有個平台比我發洩下。"},{"pid":"fabe23ffcacedd501fc2b589b2ba8b627736fb9a","tid":322733,"uid":101103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T06:13:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我已經唔想講前文，宜家比人fd zone左<br />\n我覺得同大家講之前我同佢係有幾夾，有幾開心都係曬鳩氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n諗左成日，究竟我做錯啲咩， 不斷反省<br />\n到左琴晚發左2個夢都有佢，訓訓下又醒<br />\n諗住訓醒就應該會覆番我，點知都係無音訊<br />\n<br />\n我真係估唔到原來已讀不回，係好心up,個心好沉重的，可能我真係唔撚識溝女啲濕鳩毒撚<br />\n<br />\n利申，淨係想呻下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你同佢講d咩先<br />\n可能唔知點覆你姐</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佢已讀不回我果句係一個問題黎，<br />\n我覺得通訊工具愈撚發達愈方便，<br />\n對我呢啲溝唔到女既人就愈殘酷。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n起碼有得同佢吹下水<br />\n好過冇呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n愛若難以放進手裡　何不將這雙手放進心裡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唉&hellip;日日番工放工，心真係好累<br />\n唔想係同事，朋友面前成日扮無事<br />\n<br />\n就算佢未已讀不回前，<br />\n我同佢都有好撚多隱憂係無機會的<br />\n只係我一直以快沉又快沖既態度去中個頭埋去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以我真係自己攞鳩黎衰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n夠鐘啦，帶番個面具去迎接班同事啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e533b82aaf4ea9291a3cccd19a0c2ea93a1179f","tid":322733,"uid":66825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T06:14:46.000Z","msg":"明白的"},{"pid":"fe8c408960577b15293dd918c7e4e594a00100c1","tid":322733,"uid":309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T06:16:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"eaf095d5cf4dfbe2061605e97ff0eef3fb29d35a","tid":322733,"uid":101103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T14:13:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>明白的</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}